# !Pitch

## Created By: Sharon Maswai

##  Description

This app enables you to sign up as a user then create pitches and see them displayed. Other users can see your pitch,  and comment on it.

## BDD

| Behaviour | Input  | Output |
| -- |-- |--|
|Signing up| Click sign up| Display registration form|
|Signing in|Click sign in |Login form is displayed|
|Add pitch|click add-pitch then sign in|Pitches form is displayed|
|Display pitches|click view pitches|Created pitches are siplayed|


## Bugs

At the time of deployment there were no known bugs.

## Technologies used

HTML

CSS

Python3.6

Flask

Bootstrap 4


## Running app

In the terminal:

$ ./start.sh

